{"tid":2387304,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"行街被「啊哈」！盧冠廷唔Like成名作《天鳥》","createTime":"2021-01-30T08:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T09:57:51.000Z","uid":172248,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c6f31fce5dbbe93f7495e76b2fa63b2c59541502","tid":2387304,"uid":172248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T08:21:05.000Z","msg":"藝人盧冠廷、陳健安（On仔）及樂隊ONE PROMISE為ViuTV節目《歌手&bull;門》任嘉賓大談音樂路，盧冠廷笑指雖然《天鳥》是自己成名作之一，但該曲卻曾令他感到十分尷尬：「一入到茶樓或者對面街見到我都會「啊哈」，令我覺得超尷尬同好驚，所以真係好唔鍾意呢首歌。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://viu.tv/encore/singer-door/singer--doore15gai-sing-je-moon--lo-goon-ting---chan-gin-on---one-promise-ii\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fviu.tv%2Fencore%2Fsinger-door%2Fsinger--doore15gai-sing-je-moon--lo-goon-ting---chan-gin-on---one-promise-ii&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=f398f324\" target=\"_blank\">https://viu.tv/encore/singer-door/singer--doore15gai-sing-je-moon--lo-goon-ting---chan-gin-on---one-promise-ii</a><br />\n03:00 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50640e8e6d7570b65ecb3fadd8a86e3f320ae426","tid":2387304,"uid":60412,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T08:26:44.000Z","msg":"啊哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2084a48938bd6cd6113b5bc8351395b9cf45c9bb","tid":2387304,"uid":4574,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T08:37:18.000Z","msg":"苦海翻起 啊哈 愛恨"},{"pid":"582e867c98e9a778c84bc96c97f6c0e8b1335de7","tid":2387304,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T08:46:49.000Z","msg":"Aha <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5495fad44194fc1f9aee3ee3034979906532e884","tid":2387304,"uid":127425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T09:17:42.000Z","msg":"我要飛往天上~"},{"pid":"9d843a267115218df30453440e226a9692896f62","tid":2387304,"uid":35221,"like":0,"disli